{"cacheTime": 1595231028, "baseUrl": "https://kater.me/d/79271", "title": "這是什麼", "content": [{"author": "一番星", "body": "\n<p>\n<iframe allow=\"autoplay *\" allowfullscreen=\"\" data-s9e-mediaembed=\"twitter\" onload=\"var c=new MessageChannel;c.port1.onmessage=function(e){style.height=e.data+'px'};contentWindow.postMessage('s9e:init','https://s9e.github.io',[c.port2])\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://s9e.github.io/iframe/2/twitter.min.html#1276843109381332994\" style=\"background:url(https://abs.twimg.com/favicons/favicon.ico) no-repeat 50% 50%;border:0;height:250px;max-width:500px;width:100%\">\n</iframe>\n</p>\n"}, {"author": "Soro", "body": "\n<p>\n 模擬動作跟捕捉動作吧\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "一番星", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"814786\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/79271/2\">\n Soro\n </a>\n 好詭異又好酷\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "Soro", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"814788\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/79271/3\">\n 一番星\n </a>\n 這些虛擬人物唱唱跳跳後面也有一個人去飾演\n <br/>\n (你看真人身上的衣服，是跟感應器相對的)\n <br/>\n 相對的這個技術普遍也應用於遊戲了\n <br/>\n 電影也有用到\n <br/>\n 這就是遊戲角色越來越生動的原因\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "SmallYue", "body": "\n<p>\n 動態捕捉 連手遊也開始用了嗎\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "一番星", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"814805\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/79271/5\">\n SmallYue\n </a>\n 那是手遊ㄇ\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "Soro", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"814805\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/79271/5\">\n SmallYue\n </a>\n 我不知道欸 但是電腦/主機有用了\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "SmallYue", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"814806\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/79271/6\">\n 一番星\n </a>\n 好像不是遊戲畫面 看到偶大就下意識的認為是手遊了 沒想到是非官方的同人作品==\n </p>\n"}]}